content.detailedDescription:
It would be lengthy and tiresome.  the 2nd land sighting was frightening,so frightening at night that our beagle that loved to go out for a walk i dragged to our front door towards the glowing object on the top of the mountain(hill) and was so frozen in fright that it was spread eagle, dragged on its stomach and peed itself all the way to the door.
on this occassion, as a mechanical engineer student was also frightened and plans to go to the top of the hill the next morning with my dad was all forgotten the next morning and not remembered until after his death in 1986.  it was a live pulsating ellipse on the top of the desolate hill.  on another occurrence a dozen  of us were one our private ice pond and observed the white disc moving slowly/stopping/accelerating toward new york at incredible speed.
  the third sighting was a few years later over culver lake in nj and i have three slides of it, the last slide distinctly showed a domed saucer shape with what appeared to have three small pods on the underside.  i was an aerospace/optical engineer at the time and had our laboratory study the slice for grain faults and such and there was not any signs of film problems.
  very hard at my age to type so that is about it.  as this was in the 1950's and 1960's there was no one to report it to.  i could try and find the 3 very old 35mm slides over culver lake nj.
content.summary: First event viewed by a dozen, including 3 engineers. 2nd on ground 300 feet from our house.

content.detailedDescription: I was watching the iss fly-by. it was visible 273 degrees (w) and due to fly over above starting at 21:34 ending about 9 minutes later. i was using my iphone app, iss spotter.  i had not used the app for at least 3 months but earlier that day as it appeared to be going to be a clear sky i thought i would set its alarm to remind me as there was a viewing opportunity that night.  at the time (late afternoon) i was considering using my nikon d700 camera with 300mm lens to photograph it but thought i wouldn’t bother as it would just probably end up being a white dot on the screen.  i was working on my pc when the alarm went off possibly 5 minutes before the iss was due to fly over.  i went down stairs and asked (half jokingly as i knew they would say no) my wife and daughter if they wanted to come out and see the iss fly over.  i was right they were watching a film.  i was in my garden and using the app located where i should stand to get the best view of it as i’m surrounded by houses.  to the predicted second i saw the iss in the west at 273 degrees about 40 degree elevation.  just as it peaked above my head i moved around to my patio (10 feet) to watch it go over my house directly above.  however, at 21:37 as i was looking directly up my gaze was diverted to 3 dim maroon coloured lights moving directly above heading south direction at a low altitude. possibly 1500-2000 feet north to south! these 3 round dim glowing red lights were silently moving in a perfect equilateral triangle formation with one of the points trailing behind.  each light was the apparent size of a traffic light viewed at 50 feet away. i saw the object for about 6-7 seconds as it flew overhead. whilst i could not see the object, it blacked out the stars thus giving the illusion it was a solid triangular shape.   i was also uncertain of its altitude until i notice the perspectives were changing.  suddenly from an equilateral shape of the triangle narrowed and the lights were no longer round but looked saucer shape (like an upturned saucer) bulging from underneath.  once they passed above and were at an elevation of about 55 degrees heading away from me in a southerly direction i noticed the trailing red light moved towards the right leading light as though it was going to barrel roll around it, again this was the illusion it gave but after consideration and trying to make sense of what i saw (as i have no explainable reference to compare it too)i think the object was slowly spinning. at that point i ran indoors to get witnesses (my wife and daughter) but when they both came out 10-15 seconds later it was gone.  the lights were not really bright but in size they we about a quarter the size of the moon.  the object was easily dismissed by its unique form and silence to be an aircraft or aircrafts and yes, it was silent! the size of the triangle if at 1500 feet away would have fitted inside the constellation, the great bear stars that form its quadrant (would make the craft 500-600 feet across, meaning the glowing 3 lights would have been about 30 feet in diameter).  if that makes sense.  the speed if at 1500 feet i would estimate to be about 300 mph but not sure except it was fast. i regularly look at the skies generally i can often see satellites, shooting stars, commercial airlines, light aircraft and helicopters flying at night as we have the london flights go past.  i’ve even seen chinese lanterns. the object i saw was heading north to south but there was a sw breeze that evening and therefore was not being blown by the wind.  the object i saw was totally unique. i would love to see it again!  i hope there are other witnesses who saw it to collaborate this statement. research on the internet lead me to believe this was the top secret tr3-b flying triangle operated by usa.
content.summary: Black triangle slowly spinning c/w with maroon 3 dim lights 1 on each corner

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving to school, waiting in stop-go traffic to enter the school driveway. i noticed this craft very high up in a clearing above the trees and road. it was white to glowing orange in the early morning sun. i could not hear any noise associated with it.  it was totally stationary for about 5 minutes - long enough for me to snap pictures. the craft was geometric. i could make out some lines that maybe looked like plane wings or " geometric segments" on the facade, but it was stationary. there was another plane flying lower, nearby. we are in a flight zone, so we see planes all the time, at many different altitudes. this craft was most definitely stationary. it was very high up, so it would be hard to tell if it was a helicopter. i have never seen a helicopter this high up.
i snapped about 3 photos, and got one image, but it is very, very small in the original photo.
content.summary: Stationary craft, reflective in morning sun, very high up, triangular to rectangular

content.detailedDescription: My son and i were sitting on my patio watching planes and meteorites when we notice some satellites.  my patio faces to the east.  i noticed a third satellite to our north which was traveling southbound.  as i told my son "there's another one" he turned and looked when suddenly it emitted a huge brilliant flash which lit up the entire night sky around it.  we were both surprised and commented we had never seen anything like that before, and wondered what it was.  it seemed strange enough to report if for no other reason than to see if this is normal for satellites.  the object continued traveling and a high speed maintaining its southern course.  we did not observe any flashing lights like we always see on planes, and it appeared to be much to high to be a plane or drone.  i wish we had caught we saw on our cell phones but it happened much to quickly.
content.summary: Looked like a satellite until we saw a large brilliant flash with lit up the entire sky around it.

content.detailedDescription: I captured sighting on my cell phone video camera from miles away through the windshield of my car.   it was middle of the night/morning and  the orb was going crazy what looked to be above seymour mt.  a local ski hill .......Orb that mutated into two at times ....I no longer have the file bu i uploaded it to youtube the next  day and as soon as i tploadef it my phone cut out and never worked again......The video is on youtube under " rapid moving orb / ufo captured above seymour mountain in vancouver bc" it looked like a flashlight from heaven being waved around by soneone

content.detailedDescription:
1.  i was upstairs watching tv and noticed a string of lights that seemed to be a bit odd.  at first i dismissed it as some sort of airplane light.  however as the object got closer, it banked at an angle and i could clearly see that it was of a triangular form and had 3 white lights at each of the corners and a bright red light in the middle.

2. what caught my attention was the straight line of lights that i noticed prior to the aircraft turning to go in a southern direction.  once i saw the object/aircraft bank and go in a southern direction is when i noticed its triangular form. 

3. being a fan of your show, i immediately thought that this was part of a "black project" and was highly confident that what i saw was a tr3a/b model

4. at first the object was going in a straight line west bound.  however within a few minutes it turned due south and that is when i could see the shape of the object/aircraft.  the triangular shape and placement of the lights immediately gave it away.  having been excited at what i witnessed, i ran down stairs and could see the object through the tree lines.  it appeared that it was landing at one of the local county airports. it also sounded as though there was a slight hum.  10/25/15 was a very clear night with perfect visibility.  i stayed outside for another 15 minutes and than saw the object go in a circular direction (i cannot estimate the distance it was from where i was standing) and go east bound.  again the triangular white lights and red light (in the center of the object) gave it away.  i do not know of any current commercial or military aircraft that has this particular light pattern.  

5.  i was very excited at what i had saw.  it confirmed what i have seen on your show plus doing my own research of top secret black project aircraft.

6. the object flew out of site.
content.summary: The object i believe is a tr3-a or tre3-b triangular shaped aircraft

content.detailedDescription:
at approximately 5:40am on 10-26-2015 i had the occasion to look out my side door and observed two circles of lights in the eastern sky approximately at a 45* angle above the horizon. all the lights contained in the circle where arranged in order from the center to outer diameter. the smaller (golf ball size) was to the left of the larger circle (basketball size)and were parallel to each other. did not see anything between the circles indicating they were attached. both light circles were observed for 10 minutes when i stopped & went inside. i did not take any pictures of what i observed. 
    the sighting was unusual & kept my interest until i went back inside my home. afterward i just wondered what it could have been.
content.summary: Two cluster of lights , one larger than another. lights formed uniformly in circles without edges

denise

content.detailedDescription: # 1 i was at home,watching the night sky as i usually do.Isaw this familiar ufo and put it in the crosshairs of my telescope 114az by meade co. #2 i have been watching this same ufo now for a few years so i can pick it out pretty easily in the night sky i know its patterns. #3 the object in question always appears at first to be star like then shortly after watching its patterns in the sky i notice its the same thing i have been watching for sometime now.#4 this object always seems to have a flicker to it in that the lights that it has flicker and is small in the beginning and its pattern always seems to start in the northern sky and goes east,after spotting it in the northern sky it always goes south until it appears to stop and hover in the eastern sky.This object has a very strange hovering pattern in that it moves in circles then goes left then goes down and then back up at the same time moving very slowly towards the east .This object always appears just after dark and can be seen  until 7;30 or saw the following morning as it did this time.I do notice that as it becomes lighter in the morning hours it takes somewhat of a shape to it but it is hard to dtermine exactly what it is at this time. #5 i find this extremely interesting and can not fatham why this has never been noticed from an observitory.I completely understand how this must sound but this must be seen......As i have said before these sightings will cease as the winter months get further along however, i dont think this object ever goes away i believe we just cant see it because of the cloud cover that is asocciated with the winter months.What do i have to do here to get someone here to view this object !!!!!!! #6 i lose sight of this object as the morning sun climbs higher and higher,it is then i always see a sort of shape to it but cannot make it out with my telescope.This object as the sun gets brighter and brighter gets dimmer and dimmer however as i have noticed all along it is always the last thing seen in the morning sky when all the other stars have gone.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Star like at first,with lights that flicker then gets brighter

content.detailedDescription:
Took my dog into my backyard to pee. after approx 3 or 4 mins i felt this urge to look up to my left to see 2 brilliantly lit objects close in proximity to each other by approx. 50-100 feet or so apart. it seemed the objects were there for awhile. i shot video and took photos then finally went back into my home, objects still hovering over the canoga park/woodland hills area in complete silence. 

i took photos of the clearly visible stars (orions belt, big & little dipper) that were to the far, far right of the objects to show a comparison of how low altitude objects were and how dim the star light was in comparison to the lit objects. 

when i first saw the objects, i thought they may have been 2 police helicopters hovering with their spot lights on but, then i realized that i would have been able to hear the rotors based on their distance from me. also, the were no strobe or flashing beacons that all aircraft have. additionally, the lights of the 2 objects were far brighter than anything i'd ever seen on an 
aircraft. 

after i took photos and watched the objects for approx 8-10 minutes, i went back into my house to go to bed. the objects were still in the sky in the same location, not making a sound.
content.summary: 2 extremely bright lit objects stationary in sky for lenghthy period no sound all stars very dim juxtaposed

content.detailedDescription: I was driving east on 635 when the entire eastern sky towards dallas lit up teal green , quite brightly. this was easy to notice since it was early morning and the sun was not yet up. i checked the weather and it was supposed to be cloudy but no lightning was in the forecast. i should mention the light was shrouded by the clouds ,so i didn't get to see what was emitting the light. i just know it was brighter and greener than any light i had ever seen . this lasted only a second but i felt compelled to report it as i've seen no trace of any news story here locally that reports an explanation.
content.summary: Teal green light. illuminated sky behind cloud

content.detailedDescription:
Dear investigator,

due to foot pain i decided to use my jacuzzi at around 2:00 am.  for pain i had taken aleve.  no drugs no alcohol.  after being in the jacuzzi for approximately 10 minutes and while staring east toward boise, i saw a dark object streak across the sky.  the object moved from north to south and was moving so fast the entire incident last about one second.  there was no trail behind the object.  there was no burning and whatever i saw appeared to be traveling parallel to the earths surface. the object or streak gave an appearance of aspirin to penny in size, but i would guess it was 20 miles or so east of my location. 

it definitely was not a plane. it also was not a bird. whatever it was it moved at what seemed near light speed, but it was dark matter. 

how do i feel. like i saw something that i can't explain. i lost sight of the object quickly as it disappeared out of view.
content.summary: Dark streak across sky. no trail.  no lights or sound  just dark object in an almost blur

content.detailedDescription: My husband, mother-in-law and i were heading out for one more smoke before bed. we went out on the back patio facing east. i come around to the patio table and notice what looks like a ball of fire. a solid nonflickering ball of perfectly circular fire. yellow in the center fading to deep red around the edges. it had been raining and the skies were finally clear. i watched the object start moving and heading up at like a 45 degree angle. i then pointed it out to my husband who pointed it out to his mother. my husband and i watched as this thing sped up. faster and faster until it got so far away we couldn't see it anymore. we were both completely baffled with no clue what it was.
content.summary: Fireball flew up then disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
1) visual and physical encounter:
my friend (a very well respected physicist) and i were camping, target shooting during the day, hiking, 4x4ing, etc in a specific area of our mountains. the time of the encounter was around 3pm when my friend first spotted the object and although my friend mentioned that the craft was not a helicopter, as i thought, but was something "very different". it didn't get close enough to see it very well and left very quickly. i asked my friend about it and he and i began talking about ufo's and such but basically let it go. at least i did. later i saw my friend doing his "meditation thing" and told him to knock it off because he was freaking me out. around 1am or so. i actually woke up due to a noise. it was a humming or pulsating type of noise but very low. i woke my friend up and he immediately went from his tent and stood where he could see the craft come from quite a ways away and stayed there until the craft came close enough to see it vividly and then, after the craft pointed a white and wide light around the area and then towards my friend, then a bluish, skinnier light on my friend. the craft then landed. i never left my tent but had a perfect view of the whole thing. unlike my friend, i was, and to this day i am, very afraid. there are reasons my friend is not afraid but, if your organization decides to speak with him, he can explain that. even though i have been telling my friend to report his experiences to your organization for a long time, i don't want any part of it because it is very upsetting. my friend finally allowed me to tell your organization about these events despite his mistrust of law enforcement, the media, etc because when he did report these items, he was ridiculed, embarrassed and at one point, was threatened. he's not afraid, as proven by the shootout he had some time back when the men who previously threatened him showed up at his home and shot at him until he started shooting back. my friend has told me that he had some type of conversation with the three beings who exited the craft that night. they kind of looked like humans but even the shortest one was probably around seven feet tall. my friend is 6'3" and pretty big so i base my measures on that. 

the "writings" my friend received right in front of me:
my friend is a physicist and developer of some technologies i don't even understand but they have to do with clean energy, water treatment, vehicle that don't use fuel or solar or batteries and a few other items. i am one of the few witnesses who saw his his tests where he created some cool but weird weather anomalies, has provided powe to two homes almost 20 miles from his technology and have seen the prototype vehicle that doesn't use batteries, fuel etc. the biggest item in my opinion is a formerly clear piece of plexiglass that has two very odd writings or carvings on it. we actually don't know what was used to put the designs on the plexiglass. this happened during a very cool experiment my friend was doing with another device he built. i don't understand the whole thing but it basically create a lot of energy and i think magnetism and created a kind of wavy area inside of the circular part of his device. among the many times i was helping me friend, he decided to, as he said, "see if his calculations and theories were correct or not", he kind of tossed the plexiglass into the center of the wavy part and almost immediately it popped out. he thought his device may have not worked until i picked up the plexiglass and was blown away by how this blank plexiglass now had some kind of carvings on it. 
my friend has allowed me to contact your organization and allowed me to give you his contact info so if you would like to know more about our experiences and his technology and devices, you can contact him by using the information i filled out. if you don't, that's ok too. thank you for your time. by the way, neither my friend or i know what the writing or carvings mean so if you find out i know my friend would really appreciate it if you let him know.
content.summary: There are 2events i'm reporting. the craft was seen by two of us but my friend had actual contact

content.detailedDescription: A friend of mine, i've known for 20 years saw this ufo while sitting at a bus stop near michigan state university. he was sitting at the bus stop already looking at the sky, because (in his words) "i was taught to dream". my friend noticed it first, and he pointed out to his room mate who was with him. a 3rd unknown man, watched it with them as well. it was moving slowly across the sky, with two separate swirling tails. none of them had any idea, as to what it could be. but the light changed shape, and it moved too slowly to be an aircraft. this light is amber or orange colored, and aircraft are only supposed to have red, green, and white lights. my friend took a very good photo of it (3000x2000), with a street lamp, and a tree for some sense of scale. my friend had an emotional reaction to this sighting, great anger at the object, but also intimidation by it. they could have continued watching it, but their bus arrived, and they left.
content.summary: Ufo moving slowly across the sky, with two separate swirling tails.

content.detailedDescription: Traveling over wolf creek, or from west to east without any sound. bright as a full moon and my father dismised it as a falling star but since then have experienced numerous falling stars. nothing i have experienced since then compares.Even a sodi light could not put out the lumens this object did so efficiently. when i woke up i thought it was the full moon (until it started moving). it cast long shadows (50ft+) on all the trees in the fields around us. i was 9years old durring that summer outside camp but it is the most vivid memory of my childhood. my astronomy college professor told me that no significant astrological event happened during this date.
content.summary: Full moon size moving slower than falling star but faster than jet or satilight

content.detailedDescription: I was at an intersection on south main near bothelo in walnut creek. i saw what appeared to be a plane at first. it was far away and had blinking red and green lights. then it seemed to have shape shifted into a big circle with a hollow center. there were lights around the circle and they were flashing in a clockwise direction. i can't remember what colors but there were many colors. the thing descended and got closer. it bounced around, hovered, zigged then zagged. it told me it was okay not to be affraid. it told me that energetically. it went from far away appearing to be the size of an airplane to close up appearing to be the size of a basketball. it was very strange. i had to turn left at the intersection so i lost sight of the object but i felt calm and safe.
content.summary: Started far away looked like an airplane. shape shifted into a circle thing with hollow center. ascended and got smaller.

content.detailedDescription:
My wife and i were driving on grandview ridge road when we saw the object, stationary in the sky to the east. it had the shape of a square, turned at a slight angle to us. in the upper center of the square was a row of green lights running up and down about 1/3 the length of the square. the green lights were flashing in sequence top to bottom. the white lights were very bright and constant.
the object appeared to be solid but it was dark and i couldn't determine if it was solid or if the light were individual objects.
we saw it for less than a minute and never thought to stop or to take pictures.
content.summary: 4 white lights in the shape of a square with green sequential lights in the upper part of the square.

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i were filming our motorcycle ride with a gopro when we were stopped in traffic for a very long time due to a roll over. as we sat there the camera captured all kinds of activity neither of us saw at the time. it wasn't until i began editing the video that i saw what happened. incredible.
content.summary: While in a severe traffic jam on the interstate, reportedly 7.5 miles long, i captured many ufos.

content.detailedDescription: Around 10 a.M. on the morning of 10-25-2015 my spouse saw "someone" walk outside of our bedroom window. i got up,and went outside to check, i found no-one, but found a very large indention in the ground in the shape of a large foot print, where the grass had been pressed into the ground and the ground had been pressed down about 1/2 inch. i showed it to her but she told me she did not think it could be a track. later that evening i noticed my trail cam at the end of my drive way was blinking red indicating it had low/dead batteries. i thought that was strange as i had just changed them the day before. they normally last up to two weeks on a charge. so i retrieved the camera, and replaced the battery and took the memory card out of it to look at it. at 6:16 a.M. it showed a very weird set of lights that seemed to be moving at a high speed hovering above the ground, going past the camera, it got one shot of the object, then one shot of the light as it receded. then 19 seconds after the object passed the batteries in the camera went dead. this is not normal...I am not sure what went on here, or what the camera captured. i am not claiming aliens, but i honestly have no explanation for what the picture is, or how the camera batteries were drained, and who or what was outside my house this morning that left a 20" footprint.
content.summary: Caught picture on trail cam, then batteries were sucked dead within 19 seconds.

content.detailedDescription: While observing the fourth of july fireworks, me & a couple others noticed bright red orange ish orbs appearing & disappearing along with what seemed like large clear oval disc shaped bubbles that seemed to appear alot closer to us than the orbs were...This lasted for about an hour or so. after the fireworks were over these strange orbs & bubble like formations disappeared.
content.summary: Bright red orange ish orbs ascending & descending becoming one then branching out into multiples

content.detailedDescription:
My family and i were sitting in the outdoor spa when i heard a roar in the sky and my wife and daughter commented about a light in the sky. i looked up and was surprised to see a rocket like craft ascending into the sky. i have seen the u2 aircraft climb straight up and this craft did this. i am a field support engineer for an aviation company and understand flying aircraft- this was a rocket headed for orbit as it flickered and became smaller with accompanying rocket sounds. during the event, we noticed a small light separate from the rocket and go towards the west- it appeared like sparks at first. i observed the rocket until it disappeared as it climbed, growing smaller. my wife then commented that there was a parachute up in the sky. i looked up and saw what i would characterize as a jet airplane going from north to south at a high rate of speed towards the north of my location. i followed the craft visually and determined that 1) it was moving at a high rate of speed and 2) was illuminated as a bright light - not like any aircraft i am familiar with. i began to track the craft and videoed it with my iphone video. it sped to the south of my location and i videoed several clips. it then made a full circle maneuver in the sky and continued to the south. the light then disappeared. i reviewed the videos i took and was very surprised to see no view of the sky, but close up of the fence and grass. my daughter was in the hot tub behind me as i filmed and watched as i was filming this event and stated she saw the sky on my screen. what was recorded did not match what was seen. videos attached.

doug bowlsby

textron aviation field service engineer.
content.summary: Light traveled to the south
